00:17:36.117 --> 00:17:38.657
Chul Min got a call from someone in Jeju Island.

267
00:17:39.657 --> 00:17:42.557
- Where is she? - A school in Hadong.

268
00:17:42.557 --> 00:17:45.567
If we leave now, we'll arrive when the school opens.

269
00:17:52.036 --> 00:17:53.877
She's alive.

270
00:17:57.946 --> 00:17:59.706
I'll make her pay.

271
00:18:18.167 --> 00:18:20.067
This must not be it.

272
00:18:21.167 --> 00:18:24.867
It's okay. We can just turn back. Don't worry.

273
00:18:34.817 --> 00:18:35.877
What?

274
00:18:39.347 --> 00:18:40.456
What's wrong?

275
00:18:44.756 --> 00:18:46.057
Just a moment.

276
00:19:00.236 --> 00:19:01.577
Oh no.

277
00:19:08.617 --> 00:19:10.147
The battery died.

278
00:19:13.716 --> 00:19:16.087
(No service)

279
00:19:18.157 --> 00:19:22.627
Jin Jin, I'll go and get help. Wait in the car for a bit.

280
00:19:23.327 --> 00:19:24.667
No, I'm scared.

281
00:19:27.167 --> 00:19:30.506
Then count 100 giraffes very slowly. I'll be right back.

282
00:19:30.667 --> 00:19:32.867
- No. - Will you stay here all night?

283
00:19:34.077 --> 00:19:35.907
Okay, don't be long.

284
00:19:36.377 --> 00:19:37.776
Wait just a bit.

285
00:20:01.966 --> 00:20:03.067
One,

286
00:20:04.407 --> 00:20:05.436
two,

287
00:20:06.837 --> 00:20:07.907
three...

288
00:20:08.307 --> 00:20:09.307
Five,

289
00:20:10.677 --> 00:20:11.677
six...

290
00:20:12.476 --> 00:20:13.506
22,

291
00:20:14.946 --> 00:20:15.976
23...

292
00:20:16.946 --> 00:20:17.946
62,

293
00:20:19.186 --> 00:20:20.246
63...

294
00:20:22.387 --> 00:20:23.456
98,

295
00:20:25.627 --> 00:20:26.786
99...

296
00:20:50.587 --> 00:20:52.117
I found a house.

297
00:20:52.446 --> 00:20:53.647
Can you walk?

298
00:20:54.317 --> 00:20:55.387
Hang on.

299
00:21:02.026 --> 00:21:03.127
Watch your head.

300
00:21:14.706 --> 00:21:18.946
What are you two doing here so late at night?

301
00:21:19.706 --> 00:21:22.716
Sorry. We got lost, and my car broke down.

302
00:21:23.147 --> 00:21:26.046
Would you mind letting us stay the night?

303
00:21:26.387 --> 00:21:28.516
Sorry. There's no spare room.

304
00:21:29.317 --> 00:21:32.026
We didn't warm it up, so it's freezing.

305
00:21:32.127 --> 00:21:33.427
You can't sleep there.

306
00:21:34.496 --> 00:21:37.897
You'll have to sleep in our bedroom.

307
00:21:37.897 --> 00:21:40.226
We wouldn't mind though.

308
00:21:40.597 --> 00:21:42.036
Would it be all right?

309
00:21:50.107 --> 00:21:51.476
We don't mind.

310
00:22:16.567 --> 00:22:17.837
Sleep well.

311
00:22:55.776 --> 00:22:57.006
Jin Jin's...

312
00:22:59.046 --> 00:23:00.546
genuine,

313
00:23:01.246 --> 00:23:02.446
kind,

314
00:23:03.917 --> 00:23:05.716
wise, and warm.

315
00:23:12.286 --> 00:23:13.486
Come on.

316
00:23:13.587 --> 00:23:15.097
I feel tipsy.

317
00:23:16.296 --> 00:23:18.266
- Come on. - Wait.

318
00:23:19.266 --> 00:23:20.327
(Anthony fan meeting)

319
00:23:21.036 --> 00:23:23.337
Anthony, keep up.

320
00:23:27.337 --> 00:23:29.307
I bet she'll be watching.

321
00:23:31.077 --> 00:23:32.607
It wasn't for long,

322
00:23:32.877 --> 00:23:35.117
but I'm grateful for the time I spent...

323
00:23:35.776 --> 00:23:38.647
as her husband. I was happy.

324
00:23:44.587 --> 00:23:45.786
From now on?

325
00:23:48.127 --> 00:23:49.427
I guess...

326
00:23:51.927 --> 00:23:53.996
I'll be her fan now.

327
00:23:58.436 --> 00:24:01.837
I clearly remember our first meeting.

328
00:24:07.847 --> 00:24:11.986
It was the moment my dream came true.

329
00:24:13.587 --> 00:24:17.226
I'd spent 20 years of my life smiling...

330
00:24:17.327 --> 00:24:19.427
and crying with him.

331
00:24:20.026 --> 00:24:23.327
He comforted me and gave me courage.

332
00:24:24.966 --> 00:24:27.167
Every single second we spent together...

333
00:24:27.796 --> 00:24:29.466
meant a lot to me.

334
00:24:33.776 --> 00:24:35.107
From now on?

335
00:24:36.706 --> 00:24:38.246
I'll cheer him on.

336
00:24:39.746 --> 00:24:41.417
As I always did.

337
00:24:48.157 --> 00:24:50.117
(Thank you for supporting Anthony and Sa Jin Jin.)

338
00:25:09.137 --> 00:25:11.046
(Children of 20th Century/20th Century Boy & Girl)

339
00:25:11.147 --> 00:25:14.317
Her name's Sa Ho Sung, and she's in her late 30s.

340
00:25:14.317 --> 00:25:17.077
A young lady lives alone behind the sacred tree.

341
00:25:17.077 --> 00:25:20.317
Let's stop. I think I've had enough of the entertainment industry.

342
00:25:20.657 --> 00:25:21.917
Just one more job.

343
00:25:21.917 --> 00:25:23.986
- The bodyguard. - He's on his way.

344
00:25:24.087 --> 00:25:25.127
Who is it?

345
00:25:25.127 --> 00:25:27.927
Mom, when did you decide to get married?

346
00:25:27.927 --> 00:25:29.026
Come home.

347
00:25:29.026 --> 00:25:30.097
This is home.

348
00:25:30.097 --> 00:25:31.827
Come home. Mom's waiting.

349
00:25:31.827 --> 00:25:33.696
She got sick waiting for you.

